<LG>
<L>When BRITAIN fir&s;t impelled by pride,</L>
<L>U&s;urp'd dominion o'er the main,</L>
<L>Ble&s;t peace, &s;he vainly threw a&s;ide,</L>
<L>And gave her &s;ons the galling chain.</L>
<L>View Britannia, Britannia view the waves,</L>
<L>On which thy darling &s;ons are &s;laves.</L>
