<LG>
<L>The nations now more ble&s;t than thee,</L>
<L>Shall &s;ee their haughty de&s;pots fall,</L>
<L>What time thy haple&s;s fate &s;hall be,</L>
<L>The &s;corn and pity of them all.</L>
