<PB N="68" REF="69">
<L>Nor let <HI>half Patriots</HI> (tho&s;e,</L>
<L>Who <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> from every bla&s;t of power which blows,</L>
<L>Who with tame cowardice familiar grown,</L>
